des: Get In and Get Busy with the Chamber of Commerce of Cape Coral. Serving Cape Coral, Florida for more than 60 years, we are a champion for business and advocate for community. We are committed to engaging and responding to the needs of our members and our community while adding value to the health and vibrancy of our community. We are committed to bringing local businesses together in a single voice to support excellence and quality to help enhance our members and our city's economic prosperity. How can we help you?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
